nies like Amazon and Google to gauge interest in that local rights package.=
 It=E2=80=99s possible that Fox Sports would be interested in adding the Ho=
me Run Derby to its MLB All-Star Game coverage. (The NBA, under its expirin=
g deal, sells its entire All-Star Weekend to Warner Bros. Discovery, which =
